DataType m_type

Detailed Description

DataItem is used to represent data of a provider. Provider, Number, String, WString, PhoneNumber, Date, Time, DateTime and GenericObject classes are supported. DataItem always contains an object of one of these types but can be reused when storing new data inside the object. NOTE: Do not subclass.
